      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a truly specimen-grade example of automotive engineering. This unit features a high-revving powerplant with optimized volumetric efficiency and a razor-sharp throttle mapping that ensures instantaneous power delivery across the entire rev range. The chassis remains exceptionally stiff, preserving the original factory torsional rigidity, while the suspension geometry has been meticulously dialed in to eliminate any lateral deflection during high-G cornering. Every fluid cycle has been strictly adhered to, ensuring peak thermal management and zero parasitic loss through the drivetrain. The paint depth is consistent with a showroom-level finish, and the cabin remains a tactile environment of absolute precision. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the discerning pilot who demands zero compromises in kinetic performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
